---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Jack" description="Learn about Jack McGhee's journey from Sydney's competitive markets to the Sunshine Coast">
  <!-- Reduced hero height -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-charcoal-light text-stone-warm py-14">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3">About Jack McGhee</h1>
      <p class="font-serif text-xl text-champagne-light italic">"Think you know property? You don't know Jack."</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Information-dense content layout -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Two-column profile section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- Image: 1 column -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal-light to-charcoal rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center sticky top-24">
            <span class="font-serif text-2xl text-champagne-light">Jack McGhee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Text: 2 columns - denser layout -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">A Journey of Excellence</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                I'm Jack McGhee, a senior real estate professional with over 20 years of experience 
                delivering premium results in Sydney's most competitive property markets. My career has 
                spanned the Inner City through to the Eastern Beaches, where I've consistently achieved 
                record prices by combining disciplined strategy with decisive negotiation.
              </p>
              <p>
                My approach is grounded in understanding buyer behaviour‚Äîhow people make decisions, 
                what creates urgency, and how to position a property to maximise perceived value. I pair 
                this with clear communication, deep market knowledge, and a calm, down-to-earth style that 
                keeps my clients informed, confident, and in control throughout the process.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">From Sydney to the Sunshine Coast</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                After relocating to the Sunshine Coast with my young family, I'm now proud to call 
                Mooloolaba home and bring metropolitan expertise to a community I've long admired. My focus 
                is simple: reduce uncertainty, protect your property's value, and deliver results that 
                exceed expectations.
              </p>
              <p>
                12 months ago, I settled in Mooloolaba, turning my frequent visits to the Sunshine Coast 
                over the past 15 years into a permanent lifestyle. With strong family ties in Buderim and 
                Mooloolaba, I bring a personal passion for the area alongside my professional expertise 
                honed in Sydney's competitive eastern suburbs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- My Approach - Dense 2x2 grid -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-6">My Approach</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          <div class="bg-stone-warm border-l-4 border-champagne rounded p-5">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">üéØ Understanding Buyer Behaviour</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
              Success in real estate comes from understanding how people make decisions. I focus on 
              what creates urgency and how to position a property to maximise its perceived value.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-stone-warm border-l-4 border-champagne rounded p-5">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">üí¨ Clear Communication</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
              I believe in keeping my clients informed every step of the way. My calm, down-to-earth 
              style ensures you stay confident and in control throughout the process.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-stone-warm border-l-4 border-champagne rounded p-5">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">üìä Deep Market Knowledge</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
              With 20+ years spanning Sydney's competitive markets and now the Sunshine Coast, I bring 
              data-driven insights that protect your property's value.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-stone-warm border-l-4 border-champagne rounded p-5">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">ü§ù Disciplined Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
              Combining strategic marketing with decisive negotiation, I've consistently achieved 
              record prices by reducing uncertainty and delivering exceptional results.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services Section - Two-column dense layout -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-6">How I Can Help You</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Selling services -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-stone-cool rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-4">Selling Your Property</h3>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-charcoal-light mb-2">The Power of Emotional Connection</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
                  Australians are motivated by the lifestyle a property offers. My marketing strategies tap 
                  into these motivations using tailored storytelling, evocative imagery, and immersive 
                  campaigns that make buyers see themselves living in your home.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-charcoal-light mb-2">Proven Negotiation Expertise</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
                  Maximizing value requires deep market knowledge and strategic insight. I use data-driven 
                  approaches to position your property competitively while my negotiation skills ensure you 
                  secure the best possible price.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Buying services -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-stone-cool rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-4">Thinking of Buying?</h3>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-charcoal-light mb-2">Your Advocate, Every Step of the Way</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
                  Moving to the Sunshine Coast is a life-changing decision, and I'm here to smooth the 
                  process. Whether you're relocating from across Australia or looking for an upgrade locally, 
                  I understand what matters most‚Äîlocation, lifestyle, and long-term value.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-charcoal-light mb-2">Market Insights You Can Trust</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light leading-relaxed">
                  I combine hyperlocal knowledge with property-specific insights, ensuring you buy with 
                  confidence in one of the fastest-growing regions in the country. From Mooloolaba's relaxed 
                  beachside charm to Maroochydore's dynamic community feel, I have you covered.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to action - understated but confident -->
      <div class="bg-stone rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-graphite-light max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Whether you're buying, selling, or seeking honest market guidance, my goal is to provide 
          a structured, transparent, and highly personalised real estate experience‚Äîmaking your next 
          move both rewarding and seamless.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal bg-champagne hover:bg-champagne-dark transition-all duration-200 rounded">
          Contact Jack Today
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
